various levels of this.

00:09:16.140 --> 00:09:19.470
And so it just depends
how you process things.

00:09:19.470 --> 00:09:21.270
And I just want
everyone to know,

00:09:21.270 --> 00:09:23.970
if you identify with any of
this, you're not neurotic.

00:09:23.970 --> 00:09:24.930
You're not crazy.

00:09:24.930 --> 00:09:26.740
There's nothing wrong with you.

00:09:26.740 --> 00:09:29.100
It's a sensitivity
level that I believe

00:09:29.100 --> 00:09:30.750
is important to develop.

00:09:30.750 --> 00:09:33.030
And certainly in
massage therapy,

00:09:33.030 --> 00:09:35.890
you're feeling what's
going on in other people.

00:09:35.890 --> 00:09:38.070
And so the sensitivity is there.

00:09:38.070 --> 00:09:42.360
And we need more empathy in
our world today, desperately.

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:46.680
In places like Google to
have empathy for each other,

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:49.110
and to make your work
environment really positive

00:09:49.110 --> 00:09:52.350
and caring, I think,
is a wonderful thing.

00:09:52.350 --> 00:09:55.260
And have empathy for
the world and to bring

00:09:55.260 --> 00:09:58.950
that in is something I'm
really passionate about.

