be that to other people.

00:11:05.660 --> 00:11:07.760
So how do I work on that?

00:11:07.760 --> 00:11:11.510
And how does an empath
reconcile also sometimes

00:11:11.510 --> 00:11:13.321
being the energy vampire?

00:11:13.321 --> 00:11:14.570
JUDITH ORLOFF: Great question.

00:11:14.570 --> 00:11:16.520
That's a very humble
question, actually.

00:11:16.520 --> 00:11:18.710
If we can all ask that--

00:11:18.710 --> 00:11:21.530
There's a chapter in the
book on combating narcissists

00:11:21.530 --> 00:11:23.240
and other energy vampires.

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:27.110
And it's important if
you're sensitive to identify

00:11:27.110 --> 00:11:29.840
who are the drainers, especially
in the work environment.

00:11:29.840 --> 00:11:32.510
You can have a lot of
different kind of drainers,

00:11:32.510 --> 00:11:34.760
from the drama queen,
to the chronic talker,

00:11:34.760 --> 00:11:39.650
to the narcissist, to the
passive aggressive person.

00:11:39.650 --> 00:11:42.590
So there are many kinds
of energy vampires.

00:11:42.590 --> 00:11:45.410
And yes, we can all be drainers.

00:11:45.410 --> 00:11:47.020
We can all be energy vampires.

00:11:47.020 --> 00:11:50.150
So not to think about it as,
oh, them, or him, or her,

00:11:50.150 --> 00:11:54.590
but when we get in
to our lower selves

00:11:54.590 --> 00:11:57.830
and we get our buttons are
pushed, and we're triggered,

00:11:57.830 --> 00:12:00.080
and we're tired, and we're
not in our best selves,

00:12:00.080 --> 00:12:02.870
then we can be victims.

00:12:02.870 --> 00:12:06.950
Or we can be talkers,
or we can be just people

00:12:06.950 --> 00:12:08.940
who bring others down.

00:12:08.940 --> 00:12:10.700
And that's OK.

00:12:10.700 --> 00:12:11.960
That's part of being human.

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:14.360
And it's great to
recognize it in yourself.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:16.910
That's so great that
you asked that question.

00:12:16.910 --> 00:12:20.440
And it's wonderful also
because you can catch yourself.

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:22.340
With the awareness,
when you start

00:12:22.340 --> 00:12:24.900
getting into those
energy vampire states,

00:12:24.900 --> 00:12:26.510
you can say, OK.

00:12:26.510 --> 00:12:29.300
Or if you're a coworker,
I hope has the freedom

00:12:29.300 --> 00:12:30.620
to point it out.

00:12:30.620 --> 00:12:33.830
It's a little touchy subject,
but to say, I love you,

00:12:33.830 --> 00:12:36.580
or I respect you so much,
I love working with you,

00:12:36.580 --> 00:12:38.919
but you're complaining
a lot today.

00:12:38.919 --> 00:12:40.460
I don't know if you
have the freedom.

00:12:43.560 --> 00:12:44.060
Do you?

