Sometimes gemstones are
important to put around

00:20:58.330 --> 00:21:01.690
the desk, or
whatever centers you.

00:21:01.690 --> 00:21:02.584
It could be anything.

00:21:02.584 --> 00:21:04.250
It doesn't have to
be spiritual objects.

00:21:04.250 --> 00:21:06.550
It could be anything
that you love

00:21:06.550 --> 00:21:10.960
to create a circle of
safety around your desk,

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:13.960
like a bubble of
invisibility, if you

00:21:13.960 --> 00:21:15.220
feel like being invisible.

00:21:15.220 --> 00:21:17.950
And visualization is
very important for that,

00:21:17.950 --> 00:21:19.810
if you have an open
space environment,

00:21:19.810 --> 00:21:23.690
to visualize a protective
bubble around your environment.

00:21:23.690 --> 00:21:25.270
And although you
see other people,

00:21:25.270 --> 00:21:27.660
and you hear them talking,
and they're moving,

00:21:27.660 --> 00:21:29.630
you're in your safe place.

00:21:29.630 --> 00:21:32.620
And so what you're doing is
summoning your own inner power

00:21:32.620 --> 00:21:35.740
to create a visualization
for yourself.

00:21:35.740 --> 00:21:38.260
You're not helpless
in this environment.

00:21:38.260 --> 00:21:41.950
And when you begin
to experience that,

00:21:41.950 --> 00:21:43.420
you'll feel incredible relief.

00:21:43.420 --> 00:21:46.810
So then you can focus.

00:21:46.810 --> 00:21:50.260
When I learned to meditate, I
learned how to do it in a room

00:21:50.260 --> 00:21:52.840
where next door,
it was a Sunday,

00:21:52.840 --> 00:21:56.230
and they were having
prayer meetings with songs.

00:21:56.230 --> 00:21:58.240
And so when I was
learning how to meditate,

00:21:58.240 --> 00:22:00.910
I had a lot of external
distractions, which

00:22:00.910 --> 00:22:03.420
was really helpful for me.

00:22:03.420 --> 00:22:05.590
I learned how not
to be thrown off.

00:22:05.590 --> 00:22:09.190
And that's part of this path
of empowering sensitivity,

00:22:09.190 --> 00:22:11.080
is how do you learn
to center yourself

00:22:11.080 --> 00:22:14.240
amidst distraction and chaos.

00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:17.200
And so you can look at
it as a fun challenge.

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:18.430
And I don't know--

00:22:18.430 --> 00:22:21.970
can you hear other people
talking next to you?

00:22:21.970 --> 00:22:23.050
You can hear them.

00:22:23.050 --> 00:22:23.860
All right.

00:22:23.860 --> 00:22:26.640
Are you allowed to
wear earbuds here?

00:22:26.640 --> 00:22:31.060
OK, well, sometimes that's
helpful in playing nice music.

00:22:31.060 --> 00:22:33.380
So you can use these techniques.

00:22:33.380 --> 00:22:35.470
But most important,
energetically, you

00:22:35.470 --> 00:22:39.100
want to just focus on your
own energy, your own space,

00:22:39.100 --> 00:22:42.730
your own creativity, and
not on somebody cracking

00:22:42.730 --> 00:22:45.450
their gum next to you.

00:22:45.450 --> 00:22:47.700
Us empaths are very
sensitive to that.

00:22:47.700 --> 00:22:52.100
Coughing, cracking of gum,
clearing of the throat, all

00:22:52.100 --> 00:22:54.110
that.

00:22:54.110 --> 00:22:57.620
It's important to focus
on yourself so that you

00:22:57.620 --> 00:23:01.010
can screen out external
distractions so you

00:23:01.010 --> 00:23:03.720
could be in your best place.

