And some empaths are
emotional empaths,

00:24:01.020 --> 00:24:03.420
where you're especially
sensitive to other people's

00:24:03.420 --> 00:24:04.530
emotions.

00:24:04.530 --> 00:24:06.450
For instance, if
somebody is angry,

00:24:06.450 --> 00:24:09.780
and they come in to work
angry, you take it on.

00:24:09.780 --> 00:24:12.660
Or if somebody is depressed, you
can be sitting next to somebody

00:24:12.660 --> 00:24:14.490
and suddenly your
energy is going down,

00:24:14.490 --> 00:24:16.710
and you're starting to
feel a little depressed.

00:24:16.710 --> 00:24:19.500
And you pick up their emotions.

00:24:19.500 --> 00:24:22.320
And so empaths are
sensitive to emotions,

00:24:22.320 --> 00:24:25.470
and some are even sensitive
to physical issues, where

00:24:25.470 --> 00:24:28.650
you can pick up-- let's say
your coworker has back pain.

00:24:28.650 --> 00:24:31.110
And suddenly, your
back begins to ache.

00:24:31.110 --> 00:24:35.460
So it's just something to
watch out for in yourself.

