And then there is empaths
called intuitive empaths.

00:24:38.610 --> 00:24:41.960
And these empaths are very
open to their intuition.

00:24:41.960 --> 00:24:43.950
They're really tuned
into intuition.

00:24:43.950 --> 00:24:48.060
I personally feel, as a
psychiatrist and an empath,

00:24:48.060 --> 00:24:51.540
that it's so vital to
listen to that inner voice.

00:24:51.540 --> 00:24:55.430
And empaths have it a little
bit more open than other people,

00:24:55.430 --> 00:24:58.590
but everybody can connect
to their intuition.

00:24:58.590 --> 00:25:00.960
And that's the still
small inner voice

00:25:00.960 --> 00:25:05.370
that comes through gut feelings,
or the enteric nervous system.

00:25:05.370 --> 00:25:08.460
In the gut has actual
neurotransmitters

00:25:08.460 --> 00:25:11.350
that convey information
like the brain.

00:25:11.350 --> 00:25:15.580
So what's going on in your
gut can convey information.

00:25:15.580 --> 00:25:17.910
And so as an
intuitive empath, you

00:25:17.910 --> 00:25:20.580
can train yourself to
listen to your gut feelings

00:25:20.580 --> 00:25:21.720
about somebody.

00:25:21.720 --> 00:25:24.030
Let's say you're
hiring somebody.

00:25:24.030 --> 00:25:26.670
And they look totally
good on paper.

00:25:26.670 --> 00:25:27.750
They look amazing.

00:25:27.750 --> 00:25:29.850
But when you're sitting
across from them,

00:25:29.850 --> 00:25:32.080
your energy is going down.

00:25:32.080 --> 00:25:34.320
What is that telling you?

00:25:34.320 --> 00:25:36.870
It could be that this
isn't a good match

00:25:36.870 --> 00:25:39.820
for your particular environment.

00:25:39.820 --> 00:25:43.100
You want to have people who
are energetically harmonious.

00:25:43.100 --> 00:25:46.580
And when you hire people and
when you interview people, when

00:25:46.580 --> 00:25:49.410
you're an intuitive empath,
you can develop intuitive

00:25:49.410 --> 00:25:53.160
skills in terms of-- you look
at what they present on paper,

00:25:53.160 --> 00:25:57.320
but you also can feel
what's going on in them.

00:25:57.320 --> 00:25:58.980
So you listen to
your gut feeling.

00:25:58.980 --> 00:26:00.960
You listen to a hunch.

00:26:00.960 --> 00:26:04.890
You listen to an "aha,"
knowing that it can be waves

00:26:04.890 --> 00:26:06.660
of goosebumps that say, yes.

00:26:06.660 --> 00:26:07.770
This person is right.

00:26:07.770 --> 00:26:08.820
This is exciting.

00:26:08.820 --> 00:26:10.800
This is going to
be a great match.

00:26:10.800 --> 00:26:16.710
Or you can feel a
downward thud, or a wall,

00:26:16.710 --> 00:26:18.210
or something that's unpleasant.

00:26:18.210 --> 00:26:20.700
But when you train
yourself as an empath

00:26:20.700 --> 00:26:23.760
and as a human being to
listen to your intuition,

00:26:23.760 --> 00:26:26.800
it can give you
extra information.

00:26:26.800 --> 00:26:28.500
And so that's really essential.

00:26:28.500 --> 00:26:30.210
But what happens
is sometimes people

00:26:30.210 --> 00:26:32.340
don't listen to their
intuition and they second

00:26:32.340 --> 00:26:33.990
guess themselves.

00:26:33.990 --> 00:26:37.110
Particularly, in a very
linear environment,

00:26:37.110 --> 00:26:39.060
where you're given
information but something

00:26:39.060 --> 00:26:42.270
doesn't feel right,
I really encourage

00:26:42.270 --> 00:26:46.440
you to weigh that in
your relationship choices

00:26:46.440 --> 00:26:48.870
and in how you deal
with your coworkers.

00:26:48.870 --> 00:26:50.640
Because it will
tell you, maybe I

00:26:50.640 --> 00:26:52.710
should stay away from
this coworker today.

00:26:52.710 --> 00:26:55.110
Maybe they need
a bit more space.

00:26:55.110 --> 00:26:58.290
And it's a gift to give
them that and to honor that.

00:26:58.290 --> 00:26:59.820
They seem to be in
their own world.

00:26:59.820 --> 00:27:01.864
They seem to want
to go into a cave.

00:27:01.864 --> 00:27:02.530
All right, fine.

00:27:02.530 --> 00:27:03.488
I'll give that to them.

00:27:03.488 --> 00:27:06.060
And I won't talk to them
that much, if possible.

00:27:06.060 --> 00:27:10.050
So you can really have deep
compassion for your coworkers

00:27:10.050 --> 00:27:14.340
and for others by developing
the skill of intuition

00:27:14.340 --> 00:27:15.670
that many empaths have.

00:27:15.670 --> 00:27:18.720
And some of the specific
types-- some empaths are animal

00:27:18.720 --> 00:27:19.520
empaths.

