Empaths have a
communing with animals.

00:27:34.990 --> 00:27:39.090
With dogs, with cats, with
wild animals, with birds,

00:27:39.090 --> 00:27:43.320
some feel a very deep
connection to animals.

00:27:43.320 --> 00:27:46.050
And some have a deep
connection to the natural world

00:27:46.050 --> 00:27:46.830
and plants.

00:27:46.830 --> 00:27:49.980
They love to have plants,
they love to garden.

00:27:49.980 --> 00:27:54.030
And some have, as you said, a
connection to their dream life.

00:27:54.030 --> 00:27:56.490
Where some empaths are
dreamers and they could

00:27:56.490 --> 00:27:59.700
tune into their dreams to
get guidance in the morning

00:27:59.700 --> 00:28:01.320
by remembering your dreams.

00:28:01.320 --> 00:28:03.820
So these are all
intuitive outlets

00:28:03.820 --> 00:28:06.400
that you can really
explore and play

00:28:06.400 --> 00:28:10.000
with as a sensitive
person, as opposed

00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:13.900
to being a disembodied head
who's just a linear person, who

00:28:13.900 --> 00:28:17.230
lives up, from here up.

00:28:17.230 --> 00:28:21.010
I'm really advocating being
in your mind, and reasoning,

00:28:21.010 --> 00:28:24.400
and in the body, listening
to your intuition

00:28:24.400 --> 00:28:25.750
and your sensitivities.

00:28:25.750 --> 00:28:27.530
You can be both.

00:28:27.530 --> 00:28:31.840
And sometimes, there's a
bias against men doing this.

00:28:31.840 --> 00:28:34.090
And I have a Facebook
empath group,

00:28:34.090 --> 00:28:36.340
and it's over 11,000 people.

00:28:36.340 --> 00:28:41.800
And it may be 85%
women and 15% men.

00:28:41.800 --> 00:28:45.154
So it's harder,
sometimes, for men.

00:28:45.154 --> 00:28:46.570
I don't know how
it is-- there are

00:28:46.570 --> 00:28:50.470
a lot of men in this
audience, which is fantastic.

00:28:50.470 --> 00:28:52.100
If it's harder to
come out and say,

00:28:52.100 --> 00:28:55.630
I'm an intuitive feeling
person, and I'm also

00:28:55.630 --> 00:29:00.490
really intelligent, and smart,
and creative, and grounded--

00:29:00.490 --> 00:29:03.280
so to balance everything
for both men and women

00:29:03.280 --> 00:29:06.180
who are empaths.

00:29:06.180 --> 00:29:09.180
SPEAKER 2: So there
