employees of Google

00:33:05.982 --> 00:33:09.210
to really create and
change the world.

00:33:09.210 --> 00:33:12.510
It feels like changing
the world is here.

00:33:12.510 --> 00:33:18.680
It just feels so
important to be here.

00:33:18.680 --> 00:33:20.630
