00:33:49.730 --> 00:33:51.080
And that's beautiful.

00:33:51.080 --> 00:33:52.580
And that's nothing
to be ashamed of.

00:33:52.580 --> 00:33:54.140
And just because
you may not want

00:33:54.140 --> 00:33:56.120
to be on the football
team, and you

00:33:56.120 --> 00:33:59.180
may want to go into the
forest and meditate,

00:33:59.180 --> 00:34:02.150
that makes you
unique and beautiful.

00:34:02.150 --> 00:34:04.670
You don't have to
fit these children,

00:34:04.670 --> 00:34:07.030
these sensitive children
or Indigo children,

00:34:07.030 --> 00:34:09.800
these new children that have
a certain consciousness coming

00:34:09.800 --> 00:34:11.840
into the world, you
don't want to fit them

00:34:11.840 --> 00:34:14.449
