in your sensitivities

00:34:22.940 --> 00:34:24.199
or intuition.

00:34:24.199 --> 00:34:25.280
And that hurts.

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:27.139
I know, as an empath child.

00:34:27.139 --> 00:34:31.469
I had two physician parents
and 25 physicians in my family,

00:34:31.469 --> 00:34:35.330
