lineage of scientific thinkers.

00:34:35.330 --> 00:34:36.770
And I was a feeler.

00:34:36.770 --> 00:34:37.909
I would feel things.

00:34:37.909 --> 00:34:39.020
I would know things.

00:34:39.020 --> 00:34:43.400
I would process it differently
than a traditionally scientific

00:34:43.400 --> 00:34:45.440
person, although I did
go through medical school

00:34:45.440 --> 00:34:49.070
and I conquered that, to
balance both the intuitive

00:34:49.070 --> 00:34:51.500
and the scientific.

00:34:51.500 --> 00:34:54.000
But it wasn't how I was born.

00:34:54.000 --> 00:34:56.900
And so I've had to reclaim
that as a psychiatrist

00:34:56.900 --> 00:35:00.590
